=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/22/24225972/ai-photo-era-what-is-reality-google-pixel-9&quot;>;边缘问题的人工智能相机技巧&lt;/a>;，但 Pixel 8 Pro 仍然是一款非常好的手机，拥有彩色的 6.7 英寸 OLED 大屏幕和带有 5 倍长焦传感器的相机系统，可通过数字变焦进一步实现 10 倍放大。此外，Pixel...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239797/google-pixel-8-pro-smartphone-oneplus- open-foldable-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239797/google-pixel-8-pro-smartphone-oneplus-open-foldable-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239797/google-pixel-8-pro-smartphone-oneplus-open-foldable-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T11:05:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T11:05:17-04:00</updated><title>索尼在预告 PS5 Pro 后宣布 PlayStation“技术演示”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 DualSense Edge 控制器位于 PlayStation 5 上，具有橙色背景。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OlbQi1ngmYv_UK6fgDOGcIsoVDI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73573982/236487_Sony_DualSense_Edge_AKrales_0016。 0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;28vOHK&quot;>;索尼将于明天举办 PlayStation“技术演示”，就在几天前，我们刚刚预告了 PS5 Pro 游戏机。这场时长九分钟的直播将由 PS5 主机首席架构师 Mark Cerny 主持。 Cerny 此前透露了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/3/18/21183181/sony-ps5-playstation-5-specs-details-hardware-processor-8k-ray-tracing&quot;>;完整的 PS5 规格&lt;/a>;，将于 2020 年首次亮相。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;JS9tdJ&quot;>;该直播将于 9 月 10 日太平洋时间上午 8 点/东部时间上午 11 点/英国下午 4 点开始，并将在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/PlayStation&quot;>;PlayStation YouTube&lt;/a>; 频道。索尼尚未提供有关技术演示的任何进一步细节，但 &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.playstation.com/2024/09/09/tune-in-tomorrow-for-a-playstation-5- Technical-presentation-hosted-by-mark-cerny/&quot;>;公告&lt;/a>;紧随&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/5/24236967/sony-ps5-pro -design-leak-image&quot;>;索尼在 PlayStation 30 周年纪念图片中预告了 PS5 Pro&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;lb5OEK&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;索尼可能在忙于庆祝时确认了 PS5 Pro&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/5/24236967/sony- ps5-pro-design-leak-image&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这是 PS5 Pro 吗？&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/29/24231231/is -this-the-ps5-pro&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;索尼 PS5 Pro 是真的，开发者正在为此做好准备&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/ 15/24130716/sony-ps5-pro-specs-release-date-rumors&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;BMQ4yH&quot;>;蒙太奇包含 PS5 设计，看起来与上个月的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/29/24231231/is-this-the-ps5-pro&quot;>;PS5 Pro 泄露&lt;/a>;完全相同。 PS5 Pro 的泄露图像显示控制台上有三个黑色条纹...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237361/ps5- pro-playstation-technical-presentation-stream-mark-cerny&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237361/ps5-pro-playstation-technical-presentation-stream-mark-cerny" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237361/ps5-pro-playstation-technical-presentation-stream-mark-cerny</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Anthropic 的 Mike Krieger 希望打造值得大肆宣传的人工智能产品</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Anthropic 首席产品官 Mike Krieger 的照片插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sKeidQdA4W5iF3HbZz7MjbPoxMM=/1x0:2760x1839/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73573843/decoder__4_.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 The Verge 提供/照片：Anthropic&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Anthropic 新任首席产品官的承诺克劳德等聊天机器人的局限性以及生成式人工智能的下一步发展。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237562/anthropic-mike-krieger-claude-ai-chatbot-artifact-web-decoder-podcast-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24237562/anthropic-mike-krieger-claude-ai-chatbot-artifact-web-decoder-podcast-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24237562/anthropic-mike-krieger-claude-ai-chatbot-artifact-web-decoder-podcast-interview</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T09:15:56-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T09:15:56-04:00</updated><title>美国诉谷歌 redux：广告技术审判的所有新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一组正义秤在各种产品广告的背景前。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-eQHjIdTQNVInC21LbpW5OozcZU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73573747/STK445_ADVERTISING_STK093_GOOGLE_F。 0.jpg&quot; / >; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;谷歌和政府最近结束了他们的搜索反垄断案件，最终法官认定谷歌是垄断者。&lt;/figcaption>; p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237832/google-monopoly-Trial-ad-tech-antitrust-us-search&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24237832/google-monopoly-trial-ad-tech-antitrust-us-search" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24237832/google-monopoly-Trial-ad-tech-antitrust-us-search</id><author><name>阿迪·罗伯逊</name><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T07:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T07:00:00-04:00</updated><title> IFA 2024：最大的公告和最酷的小玩意</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Sh5IVK03qAO6UqU2goJeHU5k_Pk=/0x85:2035x1442/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73560778 /IMG_4582.6.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;IFA 科技展正在庆祝其成立 100 周年。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;可扭曲的笔记本电脑、可攀爬的机器人吸尘器，以及人工智能无所不在；以下是您需要了解的有关欧洲最大科技展上展示的所有内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24231736/ifa-2024-news -products-updates-highlights-berlin&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24231736/ifa-2024-news-products-updates-highlights-berlin" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24231736/ifa-2024-news-products-updates-highlights-berlin</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T05:18:36-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T05:18:36-04:00</updated><title> Miniroll 蓝牙扬声器是 Ultimate Ears 的回归</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;The Ultimate Ears Miniroll 扬声器被放入口袋中&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XPQpLtD1Tq2tC-H57ahWIT5z9kU=/140x0:1660x1013/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73573351/High_Resolution_JPG_MINIROLL_LIFE_Black_004.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Ultimate Ears Miniroll 现已推出黑色、灰色、粉色和蓝色配色。&lt;/em>; |图片：Logitch / Ultimate Ears&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;yQEniT&quot;>;Ultimate Ears 刚刚推出了 Miniroll，这是一款新型紧凑型蓝牙扬声器，比 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge&quot; 更便携.com/2024/6/26/24185957/ue-everboom-boom-4-wonderboom-megaboom-features&quot;>;该公司的 Boom 品牌&lt;/a>;阵容。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20240909869813/en/Sound-On-The-Go-Ultimate-Ears-Unveils-MI​​NIROLL-an-Ultra-Light-Portable-Speaker-With -Strap&quot;>;Miniroll 的售价为 79.99 美元&lt;/a>;，是 Ultimate Ears 提供的最小且最实惠的蓝牙扬声器，并恢复了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com 使用的圆盘设计/2015/6/16/8786789/logitech-ue-roll-bluetooth-speaker-hands-on&quot;>;公司已停产的 Roll&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/Circuitbreaker/2016 /5/24/11758604/ultimate-ears-ue-roll-2-bluetooth-speaker-announced&quot;>;Roll 2 产品&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;PX9rWR&quot;>;顾名思义，熟悉的外形尺寸已缩小至直径约 4 英寸（105 毫米），厚度为 1.9 英寸（48 毫米），使其更容易放入口袋或较小的包中。 Miniroll 重 9.8 盎司（279 克），仍然配有内置带子，可用于将其固定在包袋和皮带环等物品上。 Ultimate Ears 还表示，该扬声器的“防摔”性能高达...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239682/ultimate- Ears-miniroll-bluetooth-speaker-price-availability&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239682/ultimate-ears-miniroll-bluetooth-speaker-price-availability" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239682/ultimate-ears-miniroll-bluetooth-speaker-price-availability</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T02:39:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T02:39:00-04:00</updated><title> Apple 的“It&#39;s Glowtime”iPhone 16 发布会有哪些值得期待的内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 的“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动中发光的 Apple 标志的官方艺术作品。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/e1Ai4JbeeFVHIEg00CelWszFcSA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/ cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73562704/GLOWITME_APPLE_.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZcOG8G&quot;>;Apple 已做好准备发布 iPhone 16，这肯定是迄今为止功能最强大、相机最好的手机（至少对于 Pro 机型而言）。预计它也将成为首款搭载 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209910/apple-intelligence-ios-18-preview-siri&quot;>;Apple Intelligence&lt; /a>; 全面。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;qyxhRk&quot;>;除了 iPhone 16 系列以及一系列新手表和 AirPods 之外，苹果预计还将展示更多人工智能功能，例如理解什么的能力以及 6 月份在 WWDC 上推出的功能，其中包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209910/apple-intelligence-ios-18-preview-siri&quot; >;升级的 Siri&lt;/a>;、图像生成、AI 重写和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24209024/apple-ios-18-1-developer-beta- iphone-call-recording-transcription&quot;>;通话录音和转录&lt;/a>;功能。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;lOEYKO&quot;>;“glowtime”一词可能是指出现在屏幕边缘的发光效果。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208732/apple-intelligence-ai-ios-18-1-developer-beta-launch-iphone 中激活 Siri 时的屏幕&quot;>;iOS 18 的最新开发者测试版&lt;/a>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event- september-iphone-16-date-time-live-stream-watch-how-to-rumors&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event-september-iphone-16-date-time-live-stream-watch-how-to-rumors" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event-september-iphone-16-date-time-live-stream-watch-how-to-rumors</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-08T16:14:07-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-08T16:14:07-04:00</updated><title>这些新的 Aukey 无线充电器配有冷却风扇</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/pBCULfi6Zvb9nDsVIyo0u-bh9LY=/95x0:2504x1606/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73572559/Aukey_chargers.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;AUKEY&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;q9xhvD&quot;>;Aukey 首次亮相&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.prnewswire.com/news- releases/aukey-unveils-omnia-frez-cooling-system-with- Three-new-wireless-chargers-302239639.html&quot;>;三款新型磁性无线充电器&lt;/a>;，位于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2024/9/3/24231736/ifa-2024-news-products-updates-highlights-berlin&quot;>;柏林 IFA&lt;/a>; 配备风扇，让您的手机在充电时保持凉爽。该公司表示，这意味着充电器，称为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aukey.com/products/aukey-magfusion-3-in-1-15w-qi2-mfw-certified-magnet-fast-wireless -charging-station&quot;>;MagFusion 3 合 1 Pro&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aukey.com/products/lc-g10-magfusion-gamefrost-magic-wireless-charger- with-active-cooling-system?_psq=magfusion&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot;>;MagFusion GameFrost&lt;/a>;，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aukey.com/products/hd-mc13a-magfusion-dash -pro-magnet-wireless-charging-phone-mount-with-active-cooling-system&quot;>;MagFusion Dash Pro&lt;/a>;，也能更快地为您的手机充电。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Rrfrhf&quot;>;这三款产品均采用 Qi2 标准，这意味着可为兼容手机提供高达 15 瓦的充电功率，并向后兼容普通 Qi 设备。 Aukey 声称，与“传统无线充电器”相比，它们的充电温度可降低高达 68 华氏度。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;9Tz2i6&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;美的新款厨房电器率先使用 Ki 无线电源&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/6/24237424/midea- wireless-power-kitchen-induction&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这款 Qi2 车载支架比 MagSafe 充电器便宜，并且可以为您的 iPhone 15 快速充电&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/1/24/24049436/esr-qi2-car-mount-15w-wireless-iphone-charging-mag-safe&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= &quot;DGX44l&quot;>;MagFusion 3 合 1 Pro 支架可以同时为 iPhone、AirPods 和 Apple Watch 充电。它还可以在 30 度范围内上下倾斜。 MagFusion GameFrost 是...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/8/24239204/aukey-omnia-frez-wireless-charger-cooling- fans-iphone-magsafe&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/8/24239204/aukey-omnia-frez-wireless-charger-cooling-fans-iphone-magsafe" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/8/24239204/aukey-omnia-frez-wireless-charger-cooling-fans-iphone-magsafe</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry></feed>